Welcome to Future Histories, my name is Jan Gross and my guest today is Jesper Burns.

00:05.700 --> 00:13.600
Jesper is an author, managing editor at Commune Magazine and lecturer at the University of California, Berkeley.

00:13.600 --> 00:21.500
