00:30.800 --> 00:40.000
One of the reasons I wanted to talk to Jesper is that I wanted to find out if there is room for a synthesis between what he describes as

00:40.000 --> 00:48.000
planarchy and another approach towards planning that has been discussed in future histories quite prominently,

00:48.000 --> 00:54.900
namely that of Daniel E. Serow's author of Information Technology and Socialist Construction,

00:54.900 --> 01:05.200
The End of Capital and the Transition to Socialism, who I had the pleasure of welcoming as a guest in double episode 31 and 32.

01:05.200 --> 01:14.600
