01:23:02.400 --> 01:23:15.400
very much encapsules a like a mode of a specific mode of power that relies on crisis and the ongoing crisis that you speak of.

01:23:15.400 --> 01:23:22.400
And I'm not sure whether this will lead us to to what you hope for, maybe.

01:23:22.400 --> 01:23:36.400
And on the other hand, I, I, I absolutely like the kind of optimism that lies within within your notion as well.

01:23:36.400 --> 01:23:47.400
